article_title: House votes to repeal DC birth control law
article_text: Federal regulators may ultimately approve the megamerger of Aetna and Humana, but the resulting insurance behemoth will not be welcome to do certain business in Missouri.

article_metadata.sailthru.author: Billy House
article_metadata.description: Shortly before midnight Thursday, without fanfare, the U.S. House voted to repeal a Washington D.C. law that will prohibit employers from discriminating against workers who obtain abortions or use birth control.
